## The Edge That Compounds Over Time

The real value of a Polymarket tracker compounds over time. One convergence signal might provide a modest edge on a single trade. But consistent access to smart money positioning across hundreds of markets over months and years fundamentally changes your relationship with prediction markets. You stop reacting to headlines and start recognizing patterns in how top traders respond to various scenarios. You develop intuitions about which types of markets are most susceptible to convergence signals and which remain genuinely uncertain even among experts.

The prediction market ecosystem is maturing rapidly. What was once a niche activity for crypto enthusiasts has become a significant force in how information about future events gets priced. As more sophisticated capital enters the space, the advantages of systematic tracking will only grow. Those who build tracking habits now will be better positioned to navigate an increasingly competitive landscape.

